headline: Goldman Sachs Pounds the Table on 2 Quality Stocks Amid Heightened Volatility
summary: If there’s anything predictable about President Trump, it’s that he’ll bring unpredictability with him wherever he goes. That’s clear in his trade and tariff policy, with his threats and on-again, off-again tariffs directed at Canada and Mexico and his imposition of higher tariffs against Chinese imports.
